                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17191014-22-off108 t17191014-22-cd110"></join> last. The Prosecutor deposed that between 9 and 10 a Clock the Night aforesaid being in a Coach in the middle of the <placeName id="t17191014-22-crimeloc111">Pall Mall</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17191014-22-crimeloc111" type="placeName" value="Pall Mall"></interp>
